metadata.name: NYC HiberNation
metadata.description:
In an historic moment for mankind an octagonal section of Manhattan detaches and rises above the rest of the city, revealing a gargantuan android head from below the surface. Accelerating off into space the android takes with it, itâ€™s captive population, and leaves behind a giant crater and an astonished world.

In this first release, NYC HiberNation, the people of NYC are put into a state of 'cryo-sleep' through the simulated winter months.
